data.meta_description: Private 1st Class Kevin Vereen, Jr., assigned to Signal, Intelligence, and Sustainment Company, Headquarters and Headquarters Battalion, 4th Infantry Division, poses for portrait at Fort Carson, Colorado, May 30, 2019. Following in his father's footsteps, Vereen said that he did not imagine that a dream to be a professional football player would lead him to a career in the military. (U.S. Army photo by Sgt. Daphney Black)
